==English==

===Etymology===
From [[nag]] + [[ware]] a contraction of [[software]]

===Noun===
'''nagware'''

#{{cattag|Internet}} Software that frequently requests a payment to the authors, assuming that payment will obtain a copy of the software that doesn't annoy the user anymore about the payment. 


